Structure Explanation:

| Section           | Purpose                                |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| `manifest`        | Extension config hash (MV3 critical)   |
| `core`            | Background, content, offscreen scripts |
| `security`        | Self-protected integrity files         |
| `computer-vision` | OCR and detection modules              |
| `ui`              | Interface components                   |
| `wasm`            | Binary WebAssembly modules             |
| `metadata`        | Build statistics and signing info      |
| `verification`    | Runtime check behavior                 |


Security Features:
critical: true → File required for extension operation
selfProtected: true → File contains own integrity checks
binary: true → Non-text file (WASM)
shutdownOnCritical: Extension disables if critical file tampered


Build Integration:

# Generate checksums during build
node build/scripts/generate-checksums.js --output security/integrity/checksums.json